item.description:
Hey Folks, Come swim (or bike and run if you like) for this early morning meetup. Does the Parking lot charge 5 Dollars this early in the morning? Not sure. I will stay for a half hour but other hard core people will swim longer.

Please be careful with the weather. We will be there rain or shine but you should bring warm clothing for when you get out.

We will meet near the changing rooms by the water.
item.name: Walden Pond Early Morning Swim
